snippet.title: [2022/09 WR speedrun] Yoiyami Dancers 'Rumia, Lunatic, no items possessed' 15:39.1 [Touhou]
snippet.description:
Rumia is so cute.
This speedrun was completed without using or possessing any items at all, including the No-Item Mark. (In this category, it is slower than with the No-Item Mark because items must be avoided.)

version 1.3.0

Other videos I've posted (TAS) : https://www.nicovideo.jp/user/56935712/series
Other videos I've posted (Speedrun) : https://www.speedrun.com/user/tas_suki

#Touhou #ヨイヤミダンサーズ #RTA #YoiyamiDancers #Speedrun
